item.title: Generate random data using GenFu in C#
item.description: Sometimes, a great deal of time is wasted and a large amount of redundant code is generated when creating random data, especially when writing tests. A library named GenFu has been created that takes on the responsibility of creating random data. This library is open source, and you can find its source code on GitHub.
